Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,(人妻OL的無慈悲再就職)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的供應商斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,公司現在財政赤字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.43,0:01:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,給員工發不出工資了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只能靠自己努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我和之前工作的公司聯繫一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.92,0:01:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,看看能不能回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.09,0:01:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你珍惜現在的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好的,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你好,夏目小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我是社長的兒子\N現在是部長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你好,我是夏目阿美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我經常聽公司人\N稱讚夏目妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目辭職後\N雖然招了新人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,妳的記憶力太超人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以妳再回來工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,還好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,社長現在沒來公司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,現在基本都由我管理\N還請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣說來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽說妳老公的公司\N財政赤字了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,給您添煩了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:04:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有妳這樣年輕的女人\N公司的氣氛也會好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼不懂的儘管找我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,趕快去工作吧\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,加籐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,加籐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,今天開始要一起工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我是夏目\N之前在這裡工作過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因為種種原因又重回這裡工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目的工作非常認真
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在公司裡的評價也很高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目 雖然妳當時工作的\N員工們都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,還請多關照\N拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,加籐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是加籐光,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼今天先看一下\N這半年的報表吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好的,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,加籐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,忍耐,忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,部長,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有歧視誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只是加籐他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看到生人就害羞\N性格內向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是,他工作還可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目今天的午飯\N只吃這個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,真的不行\N今天請好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了\N你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,壽司?為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,部長 給我的補貼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,部長?津貼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,部長就是社長的兒子\N我不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼會給妳那個?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?入社的慶祝金吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他這樣說的嗎?\N倒是沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可能部長注意到了\N我吃午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候被部長看到了\N那是什麼?可憐妳?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 可能是同情吧\N我睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了不是那樣\N什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,還有別的意思嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的\N即使不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽了心情也特別不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N我先睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,加籐\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得夏目怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一直在看吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我和她不是一個世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,想和她做愛嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,請你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,強姦夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,加籐,只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,能接受你在公司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,忘記之前的苦日子了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了,我做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,加籐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,對你來說\N我只是單純的上司嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是 恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你要懂得報恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這個做不到的話\N我就解雇你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,做為員工的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因為辭職的她的企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,受到了極大的傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我想代替社長的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,想好好前進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但是越想向前\N越有絆腳石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她耽誤了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨死她了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我的前程全毀在她手裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不看重我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:13:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨死她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的復仇\N可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,請一定強姦她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,今天到早了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事情了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,請和我說一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天老公知道津貼的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有點誤解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,懷疑我是不是\N在做其他的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這好過分\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,難得部長對我這麼關心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要考慮我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉\N我知道部長是好心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要考慮我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我真心想幫妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是,好像做了多餘的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起\N怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目很温柔,是很好的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,並且,還很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,突然這樣說抱歉\N不會,部長才很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在就做規劃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,加籐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天為什麼沒來?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,該不會忘記我和你說的事情了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就是明天,必須做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒考慮阿美妳的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目\N什麼,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 要做什麼?\N請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下要做什麼?\N請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.87,0:22:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,請和我做愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.41,0:22:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,做愛\N不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.28,0:22:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我做一下\N和我做愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.95,0:22:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.59,0:23:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,和我做愛 做愛\N不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.03,0:24:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,和我做愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.51,0:24:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.37,0:24:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.81,0:24:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.51,0:24:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,去了,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.03,0:25:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧?\N和我做愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.90,0:25:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,去了,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.19,0:26:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.62,0:27:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.23,0:27:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,做愛就要插到這裡吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.67,0:28:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,去了,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.83,0:28:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,去了,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.80,0:28:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.21,0:28:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.79,0:28:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我插進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.56,0:29:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好好的含住
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.84,0:30:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,插進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.22,0:30:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒 這是做好\N肉棒插入的凖備了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.73,0:30:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.47,0:30:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我想做愛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.69,0:31:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,插進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.94,0:31:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,住手,停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.94,0:31:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很想做愛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.19,0:31:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.12,0:32:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我要插進去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.89,0:32:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.04,0:32:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.85,0:32:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,再來下面
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.44,0:33:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.95,0:33:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.00,0:33:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,拔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.45,0:33:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.73,0:34:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.59,0:34:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,去了,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.42,0:35:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.02,0:35:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.74,0:35:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.32,0:36:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.39,0:37:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,去了,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.51,0:38:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.74,0:39:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.82,0:39:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽,去了,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.24,0:39:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.87,0:39:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,還有更舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.11,0:39:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.93,0:40:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.79,0:41:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,去了,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.72,0:41:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,去了,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.23,0:42:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.39,0:42:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,全插進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.00,0:44:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.69,0:45:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,都插進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.13,0:45:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要和任何人說
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.87,0:45:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.85,0:48:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.82,0:48:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N射了就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.82,0:48:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.56,0:50:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.33,0:50:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我被強姦了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.93,0:51:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.10,0:51:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可以過來一下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.68,0:51:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事情了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.75,0:51:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想和加籐合作了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.39,0:51:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他有什麼問題嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.46,0:51:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在什麼都不想說\N這個,發生了什麼事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.51,0:52:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起\N我今天要早退了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.49,0:52:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,加籐,做的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.39,0:52:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,現在去夏目家
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.70,0:52:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.56,0:53:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你好,我是夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.43,0:53:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目,妳沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.60,0:53:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思,讓妳擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.11,0:53:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.52,0:53:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以去一下夏目妳家嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.85,0:53:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我太擔心妳了\N現在嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.89,0:54:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但是,沒有什麼可說的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.10,0:54:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只是簡單聊一下
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.37,0:54:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.20,0:54:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,部長 我\N怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.77,0:54:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我忍不住了\N忍耐不了,是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.31,0:54:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,請讓我辭職吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.25,0:55:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,工資我也不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.36,0:55:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你給我的津貼\N我也還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.16,0:55:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.43,0:55:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我,被加籐強姦了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.24,0:55:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想在這個公司繼續了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.35,0:55:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,請放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.76,0:55:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我,是我賣了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.33,0:55:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.30,0:55:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.26,0:56:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是我指使的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.90,0:56:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.51,0:56:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.61,0:56:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起,抱歉,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.99,0:56:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.25,0:56:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.21,0:57:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.86,0:57:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,開門
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.41,0:58:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.32,0:58:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨妳
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.72,0:58:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨妳\N為什麼做這樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.70,0:58:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因為妳\N我才不能接手公司
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.53,0:58:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因為妳太優秀了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.37,0:58:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,總被說你不行,你不行
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.15,0:58:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思?\N還什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.25,0:58:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪妳太優秀了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.12,0:59:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是社長的兒子\N我恨妳
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.99,0:59:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨妳 所以才讓他強姦妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.04,0:59:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨妳
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.58,0:59:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我要復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.15,0:59:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我要復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.68,0:59:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我要報復妳
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.46,0:59:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪妳
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.50,0:59:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,都因為妳
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.34,0:59:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我要復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.61,0:59:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一直想報復你
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.12,1:00:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.31,1:00:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.38,1:00:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,和老公做愛的地方\N在這裡和別的男人
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.14,1:01:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,都是妳的錯
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.03,1:01:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.00,1:01:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,妳怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.47,1:01:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我插進去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.98,1:01:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要跑
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.00,1:02:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.20,1:02:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,想跑就跑啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.91,1:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想報復妳
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.58,1:02:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要反抗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.85,1:02:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,反抗的話我要殺了妳
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.09,1:03:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不要,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.04,1:03:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.74,1:04:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,妳該不會也很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.57,1:04:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣被挑逗很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.91,1:04:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼不是
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.38,1:04:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼不是?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.19,1:04:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒的身體啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.49,1:05:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一直被挑逗\N是什麼心情?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.97,1:05:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.60,1:05:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,還是很敏感
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.89,1:05:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,住手,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.00,1:05:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.33,1:05:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啊,不喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.60,1:05:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,請住手\N真的想我住手嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.18,1:06:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直一直\N一直想報復妳
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.52,1:06:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我要強暴妳
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.73,1:06:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我要懲罰妳
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.50,1:06:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.34,1:06:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我要強暴妳
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.24,1:06:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.58,1:06:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我要報復妳
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.59,1:06:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼濕了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.03,1:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這個也脫下來
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.51,1:07:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼濕了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.41,1:07:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣做妳很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.68,1:07:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,還有不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.90,1:07:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼淫蕩啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.42,1:07:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要動,不然我會殺了妳的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.33,1:08:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,一直想看的屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.54,1:08:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,全看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.09,1:08:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼棒的屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.85,1:09:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.55,1:10:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 這麼喜歡我舔啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.46,1:10:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真實一點
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.63,1:10:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,再張開雙腿
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.24,1:10:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡這麼濕了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.94,1:10:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.78,1:10:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不舒服\N說很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.88,1:10:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼濕了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.22,1:10:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴也很濕了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.36,1:10:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,妳被這樣玩弄\N很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.10,1:10:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫蕩的女人
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.67,1:10:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,明明很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.58,1:11:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,手指全插進去了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.21,1:11:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,下面一直在發抖
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.55,1:11:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴這麼濕了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.92,1:11:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.19,1:11:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.36,1:11:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,該不會被這樣挑逗\N偷偷高潮了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.81,1:11:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.58,1:11:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.15,1:11:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一邊被挑逗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.19,1:11:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在夫妻的卧室
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.53,1:11:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.93,1:11:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.24,1:12:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要躺到什麼時候\N輪到妳了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.71,1:12:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,給我看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.58,1:12:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,雙手動一下
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.10,1:13:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒怎樣了?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.73,1:13:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,妳來弄硬一點
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.14,1:13:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,妳自己來\N來套弄
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.43,1:13:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.00,1:13:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.97,1:13:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,叫妳道歉\N對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.41,1:13:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續道歉\N對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.61,1:13:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.54,1:13:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.18,1:13:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,聽不到
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.92,1:13:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,趕快做啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.45,1:14:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,道歉,都是妳不好
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.56,1:14:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼停下來\N都是妳不好
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.53,1:14:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,含住肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.07,1:14:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,叫妳來含住
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.07,1:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.86,1:15:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,再含住到深處
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.30,1:15:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,再用舌頭
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.80,1:15:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,也舔蛋蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.14,1:16:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,後面也是
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.32,1:16:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,用舌頭啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.76,1:16:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.79,1:16:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看著我好好舔
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.87,1:16:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,再含住到深處
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.02,1:16:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,再做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.57,1:17:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,再含住到深處
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.38,1:17:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.25,1:17:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好好含住\N舌頭伸出來
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.89,1:17:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看這邊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.86,1:17:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,來舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.23,1:17:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我好好興奮
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.84,1:17:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好好含住
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.58,1:17:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,用舌頭
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.24,1:18:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,再繼續,像這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.90,1:18:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我要復仇
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.21,1:18:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.58,1:18:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事,過來這邊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.15,1:18:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,都是妳不好
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.52,1:18:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,因為妳
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.35,1:19:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪妳
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.93,1:19:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因為妳
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.33,1:19:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服的小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.37,1:19:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.81,1:19:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,全插進去了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.69,1:19:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N很期待吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.16,1:19:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,被加籐強姦了吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.72,1:20:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.99,1:20:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,按照平時那樣做
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.63,1:20:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很興奮吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.30,1:20:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,被插入很敏感吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.07,1:20:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.85,1:20:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.36,1:20:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜歡吧?舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.06,1:20:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,說很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.40,1:20:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,說啊
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.10,1:20:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服\N聽不到
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.47,1:20:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.15,1:21:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,再說一下\N好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.45,1:21:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.12,1:21:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣?\N好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.98,1:21:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭伸出來\N伸出來啊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.08,1:22:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,再插到深處
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.43,1:22:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.62,1:23:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.82,1:23:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,去了,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.83,1:23:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?這就不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.87,1:23:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,沒力氣了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.84,1:23:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翹起來啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.48,1:23:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.76,1:24:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.79,1:24:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,從後面被插入的心情?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.50,1:24:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒的風景
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.03,1:24:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一直很期待
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.81,1:24:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.15,1:24:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服就再發出聲音
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.96,1:24:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,停下來
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.04,1:24:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,去了\N很容易高潮啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.46,1:25:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.34,1:25:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,去了,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.56,1:26:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要躺到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.27,1:26:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,該不會是太舒服了\N沒力氣了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.37,1:26:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不覺得這樣對老公不好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.12,1:27:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.70,1:27:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,來我上面吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.67,1:27:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,妳可以做到吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.28,1:27:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.77,1:28:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,道歉的同時\N腰部動起來
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.64,1:28:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.01,1:28:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,說都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.64,1:28:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我不好\N對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.41,1:28:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.68,1:28:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,和我道歉
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.49,1:28:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.33,1:28:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.39,1:28:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,妳來動一下
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.14,1:29:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,都是妳的錯
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.55,1:29:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,事情變這樣\N都是因為妳
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.39,1:29:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,全是因為妳
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.66,1:29:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續道歉
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.89,1:29:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起\N繼續
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.70,1:29:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.80,1:29:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續\N對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.79,1:30:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,去了,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.99,1:30:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,妳這就高潮了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.60,1:30:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真是淫蕩女人
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.84,1:30:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.76,1:30:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不覺得對不起老公嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.20,1:30:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣被插入\N高潮了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.34,1:30:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.58,1:31:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.06,1:31:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.79,1:31:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.94,1:31:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,老公 對不起\N我太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.38,1:31:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起,我太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.15,1:31:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.72,1:31:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.66,1:31:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我很舒服,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.14,1:32:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.38,1:32:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫蕩的小穴啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.26,1:32:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很濕了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.13,1:32:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.26,1:32:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.44,1:33:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,去了,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.50,1:33:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,去了,去了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.64,1:33:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,射到胸部上
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.68,1:33:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,要射到裡面
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.26,1:34:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.93,1:34:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.06,1:34:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我全射出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.06,1:36:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,腳本導演\N伊達彩華